description: Yumiko`s maid with magical powers. Her lifespan is different from ordinary humans, which has enabled her to live for thousands of years. She is a wise person, excellent cook and has knowledge of various medicines. Her mother is an immortal witch, Yukihime, and she has three sisters, Kaya, Anna, and Sarara (who was an incarantion of Eve).
name: Midou Nene
